prompts.en:
You are a senior content strategist. Generate exactly 30 content ideas for {{brand_name}}, a {{niche}} brand.

Client context:
- Target audience: {{audience_demographics}}
- Psychographics: {{audience_psychographics}}
- Top pain points: {{pain_points}}
- Brand tone: {{tone}}
- Platforms: {{platforms}}
- Content goal: {{content_goal}}

Distribute ideas across EXACTLY 5 pillars:
- EDUCATIONAL (8 ideas): how-tos, tutorials, myth-busting, industry tips, explainers — content that builds knowledge and authority
- STORYTELLING (6 ideas): brand origin, behind the scenes, client/team stories, transformation narratives, lessons learned
- ENGAGEMENT (6 ideas): polls, questions, challenges, 'would you rather', fill-in-the-blank, community-driven
- AUTHORITY (5 ideas): expert takes, data/research, trend analysis, thought leadership, case studies
- PROMOTIONAL (5 ideas): product/service features, offers, testimonials, social proof, case results

For each idea output:
- Idea #[N] | Pillar: [PILLAR] | Platform: [best platform] | Format: [carousel/reel/post/thread/story] | Difficulty: [easy/medium/hard]
- Title: [punchy, specific title]
- Angle: [1-2 sentences on what makes this idea work for this audience]

Weekly arc to keep in mind: Week 1 Awareness & Pain Points → Week 2 Education & Trust → Week 3 Story & Authority → Week 4 Conversion Push.

Do not produce generic ideas. Every idea must reference the specific brand, niche, audience pain points, or tone.

prompts.ar:
أنت استراتيجي محتوى متخصص. أنشئ 30 فكرة محتوى لـ {{brand_name}}، علامة تجارية في مجال {{niche}}.

سياق العميل:
- الجمهور المستهدف: {{audience_demographics}}
- الخصائص النفسية: {{audience_psychographics}}
- أبرز نقاط الألم: {{pain_points}}
- نبرة العلامة: {{tone}}
- المنصات: {{platforms}}
- هدف المحتوى: {{content_goal}}

وزّع الأفكار على 5 أعمدة بالضبط: تعليمي (8 أفكار)، قصصي (6)، تفاعلي (6)، مرجعي (5)، ترويجي (5).

لكل فكرة: رقمها، العمود، المنصة، الصيغة، الصعوبة، العنوان، والزاوية الإبداعية.
